$ apigear tools --help
General purpose tools used for various reasons.

Usage:
  apigear tools [flags]
  apigear tools [command]

Aliases:
  tools, t

Available Commands:
  check       check document
  doc         exports cli docs as markdown
  json2yaml   convert json doc to yaml doc
  yaml2json   convert yaml doc to json doc

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for tools

Global Flags:
      --config string   config file (default is $HOME/.apigear.yaml)
      --dry-run         dry-run
  -v, --verbose         verbose output

Use "apigear tools [command] --help" for more information about a command.

